{
  "stem": "19550.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 205.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I had apparently enough emotional, and psychological, and mental reserves to preserve my humanity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That hasn't, you know, never ceased to be a preoccupation, a futile one most of the times for myself and several others who were, like myself, were what should I say, aware and conscious people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one, on one occasion when we were being taken from [INAUDIBLE] to, from [INAUDIBLE] to, back to Germany we were stopped at the station of Luxembourg.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in open cars, you know, coal cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, there was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS spread out in the fields around the rails.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a young man and myself, we wanted to make a break for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Unfortunately, before we could finally manage to make a break for it, the air raid alarm was called off and suddenly the SS was coming back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And again, you have this, this interplay of the time question.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At [INAUDIBLE], I am to this day convinced that the local underground and some of the other different kind of forced laborers who were not Jews, Poles, and Czechs, et cetera, who were in the, in the area were, and particularly the French underground, were about ready to assist us if we made a move.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And again, it was an interplay of the time that just didn't work on the one hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the other hand, unfortunately, one of the leaders of our camp that we recognized as our leader, translated the warning of the camp commandant that we shouldn't try anything, word for word saying that every second man would be shot out of the line.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, we were all paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
